title: Ghosthunting With... I'm a Celebrity.avi
description:
I would normally just say....

Ghost Hunting With... I&#039;m a Celebrity.avi

But this needs explained.

This is a Most Haunted spin off

Program synopsis is as follows......

Yvette Fielding, the world&#039;s foremost ghost hunter, takes five famous former contestants on I&#039;m a Celebrity... Get Me Out of Here! to some of the eeriest places in the West Midlands. Jungle winners Christopher Biggins and Matt Willis are joined by Cerys Matthews, Dean Gaffney, and Willis&#039;s girlfriend Emma Griffiths, on their creepy ghost hunt... but how will it compare to living in the bush?

enjoy........
